videos.headline: Wallace muscles way into end zone to grab lead
videos.description: Tylan Wallace breaks some tackles to score a 40-yard touchdown, giving Oklahoma State the first lead of the night.

videos.headline: Ehlinger takes it himself to tie game
videos.description: Texas QB Sam Ehlinger shakes a defender and makes it to the end zone to tie the game 7-7.

videos.headline: Cornelius throws TD off back leg
videos.description: Oklahoma State QB Taylor Cornelius throws a perfect pass off his back leg to Jelani Woods to regain the lead at 14-7.

videos.headline: Cornelius powers way into end zone
videos.description: QB Taylor Cornelius sneaks in a 1-yard touchdown to extend Oklahoma State's lead over Texas 24-7.

videos.headline: Ehlinger's 37-yard pass sets up QB sneak for TD
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger slings a 37-yard pass to the 1-yard line to set up a QB sneak on the next play.

videos.headline: Wallace leaps over defender to grab 2nd TD
videos.description: Oklahoma State's Tylan Wallace "Mosses" a defender to grab his second touchdown of the night.

videos.headline: Oklahoma State looking strong at halftime
videos.description: The Cowboys score early and often in the first half, with Tylan Wallace hauling in two of Taylor Cornelius' three first-half TD passes.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Oklahoma State looking strong at halftime) 2018/10/27 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Ehlinger slings perfect TD pass to cut deficit
videos.description: QB Sam Ehlinger throws a dime to Keaontay Ingram to put the Longhorns back in the game at 31-21.

videos.headline: Texas inches closer on Ehlinger's 3 TD pass
videos.description: Sam Ehlinger jumps over the line and throws a touchdown at the apex of his leap to make it a one possession game.

videos.headline: Cornelius squeezes ball inside pylon for score
videos.description: Taylor Cornelius runs 10 yards and narrowly gets the ball inside the pylon to extend the lead to 38-28 with the game winding down.

videos.headline: Texas' Herman penalized during ugly ending
videos.description: Oklahoma State kneels on the final play but things get heated, including a personal foul on Texas head coach Tom Herman.

videos.headline: Gundy: 'I didn't want it to get ugly'
videos.description: Oklahoma State head coach Mike Gundy reacts to the ugly ending to the game and compliments his team's practice leading up to the upset over No. 6 Texas.

videos.headline: Herman on Gundy: 'I have no issues'
videos.description: Texas Longhorns head coach Tom Herman discusses his decision to attempt an onside kick with three timeouts left and why he stormed the field.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Herman on Gundy: ‘I have no issues’) 2018/10/28
